After dictating the second-half of the thrilling exchange, Kapaito sealed Sharks' dominance in the 82nd minute, to take his tally to 12 goalsJulius Masaba netted Sharks' first goal in the 12th minute, before Davis Agesa levelled in the 34th minuteThe win lifts Sharks to fifth place with 18 points, while City Stars remain 10th with 10 points